queries.cypher_query: MATCH (s:Scholar)-[:BORN_IN]->(ci:City)-[:IS_CITY_IN]->(co:Country) MATCH (s)-[:AFFILIATED_WITH]->(i:Institution) WHERE toLower(co.name) CONTAINS toLower('united states') AND toLower(i.name) CONTAINS toLower('university of cambridge') RETURN DISTINCT s.knownName

queries.question: Which countries have produced laureates who won prizes in both Medicine and Physics?
queries.cypher_query: MATCH (s:Scholar)-[:BORN_IN]->(ci:City)-[:IS_CITY_IN]->(co:Country) MATCH (s)-[:WON]->(p:Prize) WITH co, COLLECT(DISTINCT toLower(p.category)) AS categories WHERE 'medicine' IN categories AND 'physics' IN categories RETURN co.name AS country

queries.question: For each birth continent, how many laureates later worked at institutions on a different continent?
queries.cypher_query: MATCH (s:Scholar)-[:BORN_IN]->(bCity:City)-[:IS_CITY_IN]->(bCountry:Country)-[:IS_COUNTRY_IN]->(bCont:Continent) MATCH (s)-[:AFFILIATED_WITH]->(i:Institution)-[:IS_LOCATED_IN]->(aCity:City)-[:IS_CITY_IN]->(aCountry:Country)-[:IS_COUNTRY_IN]->(aCont:Continent) WHERE toLower(bCont.name) <> toLower(aCont.name) WITH bCont, COUNT(DISTINCT s) AS numLaureates RETURN bCont.name AS birthContinent, numLaureates

queries.question: Which scholars have affiliations in at least three different countries?
queries.cypher_query: MATCH (s:Scholar)-[:AFFILIATED_WITH]->(i:Institution)-[:IS_LOCATED_IN]->(ci:City)-[:IS_CITY_IN]->(co:Country) WITH s, COUNT(DISTINCT co) AS numCountries WHERE numCountries >= 3 RETURN s.knownName AS scholar, numCountries

queries.question: Which laureates were born in cities that host institutions they were also affiliated with?
queries.cypher_query: MATCH (s:Scholar)-[:BORN_IN]->(bCity:City) MATCH (s)-[:AFFILIATED_WITH]->(i:Institution)-[:IS_LOCATED_IN]->(aCity:City) WHERE toLower(bCity.name) = toLower(aCity.name) RETURN DISTINCT s.knownName AS laureate, bCity.name AS city
